Package: cbbreadr
Title: Quickly Access College Basketball Data
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Edwards", , "edwards1860@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8533-7504"))
Description: Quickly pull in cached data from <https://collegebasketballdata.com>. Load in play-by-play, game, roster, and other miscellanous college basketball data objects into R as dataframes. Designed for use in performing college basketball analytics and modeling work.
